<SYNC Start=2779967><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2779967><P Class=ENCC>
즉<br>자신의 신분을 숨길 필요가 있었다.
<SYNC Start=2784889><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2784889><P Class=ENCC>
10만엔을 주고.
<SYNC Start=2786889><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2788993><P Class=ENCC>
네!
<SYNC Start=2790993><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2791913><P Class=ENCC>
네!<br>아아…!
<SYNC Start=2793981><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2793981><P Class=ENCC>
앗 뭔가 생각 났어요?<br>그게 아니고...
<SYNC Start=2797902><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2797902><P Class=ENCC>
