<SYNC Start=2800905><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2800905><P Class=ENCC>
네?
<SYNC Start=2802907><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2802907><P Class=ENCC>
이대로라면 아버지에게
<SYNC Start=2804909><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2804909><P Class=ENCC>
