<SYNC Start=3158913><P Class=ENCC>
응?
<SYNC Start=3160913><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3170975><P Class=ENCC>
얼마 전 네가 말했던 것.
<SYNC Start=3172975><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3174912><P Class=ENCC>
