<SYNC Start=3235901><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3236907><P Class=ENCC>
다녀오겠습니다.
<SYNC Start=3238943><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3238943><P Class=ENCC>
다녀오세요<br> 다녀오겠습니다. 안녕.
<SYNC Start=3240895><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3249887><P Class=ENCC>
잠깐 괜찮아?<br>네.
<SYNC Start=3252907><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3252907><P Class=ENCC>
요시이군 때문인데...
<SYNC Start=3255907><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3259914><P Class=ENCC>
너에게 뭔가 말을하지 않았나?<br>에?
<SYNC Start=3262900><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3262900><P Class=ENCC>
