<SYNC Start=3451187><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3451187><P Class=ENCC>
우와! 가까이...!
<SYNC Start=3453189><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3453189><P Class=ENCC>
