<SYNC Start=5585897><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5585897><P Class=ENCC>
아닌가?
<SYNC Start=5587915><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5587915><P Class=ENCC>
어떻게 하나요?<br>어떻게 해야 돼나요?
<SYNC Start=5590915><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5591903><P Class=ENCC>
