<SYNC Start=5601911><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5603898><P Class=ENCC>
그래서 나는
<SYNC Start=5605900><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5605900><P Class=ENCC>
