<SYNC Start=5686914><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5686914><P Class=ENCC>
엣!?
<SYNC Start=5688914><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5693054><P Class=ENCC>
너가 그런<br>바보짓만 하지 않았으면...!
