<SYNC Start=5709904><P Class=ENCC>
저 녀석도 저 녀석이야.
<SYNC Start=5711904><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5715910><P Class=ENCC>
마치다 토모에씨를 죽였습니까?
<SYNC Start=5719910><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5725953><P Class=ENCC>
