<SYNC Start=5805916><P Class=ENCC>
웃...!
<SYNC Start=5807916><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5809904><P Class=ENCC>
읏…아앗...!
<SYNC Start=5812890><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5812890><P Class=ENCC>
너 따위에게...!
<SYNC Start=5814909><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5822967><P Class=ENCC>
