<SYNC Start=5848909><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5848909><P Class=ENCC>
일부러 차로<br>마중을 나와주어서요
<SYNC Start=5851912><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5859970><P Class=ENCC>
