<SYNC Start=5862907><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5870898><P Class=ENCC>
아…아앗...!
<SYNC Start=5873918><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5873918><P Class=ENCC>
우읏...!
<SYNC Start=5875920><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5887915><P Class=ENCC>
네가 그 핸드백만 버렸으면!
<SYNC Start=5890915><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5895990><P Class=ENCC>
