<SYNC Start=5915893><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5915893><P Class=ENCC>
정말 이녀석도 저 녀석도...
<SYNC Start=5918979><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5918979><P Class=ENCC>
읏!
<SYNC Start=5920898><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5920898><P Class=ENCC>
아앗...앗...!
<SYNC Start=5922900><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5929974><P Class=ENCC>
