<SYNC Start=5944902><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5946907><P Class=ENCC>
니시와키 씨
<SYNC Start=5948976><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5948976><P Class=ENCC>
