<SYNC Start=5951976><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5952913><P Class=ENCC>
왜 그렇게 했나요?
<SYNC Start=5954913><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5963907><P Class=ENCC>
