<SYNC Start=6103914><P Class=ENCC>
무엇이 아닌거야?
<SYNC Start=6105914><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6107885><P Class=ENCC>
나는...
<SYNC Start=6109903><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6158886><P Class=ENCC>
