<SYNC Start=6258900><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6264908><P Class=ENCC>
그 손만 놓지 않았다면.
<SYNC Start=6268908><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6271999><P Class=ENCC>
